@startuml

left to right direction
skinparam componentStyle rectangle

actor Client

component "API Gateway" as Gateway

component "Profile Service\n:5000" as Profile
component "Battle Service\n:5001" as Battle
component "PvE Service\n:5002" as PvE
component "Data Service\n:5003" as Data
component "PvP Service\n:5004" as PvP

database "MySQL Database" as DB

Client --> Gateway : HTTP / JSON

Gateway --> Profile : /api/profile/*
Gateway --> PvE : /api/pve/*
Gateway --> PvP : /api/pvp/*
Gateway --> Battle : /api/battle/*

PvP --> Profile : validate users
PvP --> Battle : start PvP battle

PvE --> Battle : start PvE battle
PvE --> Data : save/load campaign

Battle --> Data : store results

Profile --> Data : user data

Data --> DB : SQL queries

@enduml